you were... singing...

272
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,000
Don't tell me you heard me, too?

273
00:17:28,083 --> 00:17:30,958
Uh... Yes.

274
00:17:33,833 --> 00:17:35,666
You went to the archive today?

275
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:36,750
I did.

276
00:17:36,833 --> 00:17:39,041
Were you looking
for something specific?

277
00:17:39,875 --> 00:17:43,125
