283
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,708
You're the only
one fighting them...

284
00:17:58,791 --> 00:18:01,291
So you know this
better than anyone...

285
00:18:01,375 --> 00:18:03,291
They are incredibly strong.

286
00:18:03,375 --> 00:18:04,458
Yes.

287
00:18:04,541 --> 00:18:06,750
And you also know
the only thing capable

288
00:18:06,833 --> 00:18:08,250
of defeating these evil beings.

289
00:18:08,333 --> 00:18:10,208
The sacred blade.

290
00:18:10,291 --> 00:18:12,000
Correct.

291
00:18:13,833 --> 00:18:15,250
Your mother fought
the Elder Bairns

292
00:18:15,333 --> 00:18:18,416
using the sacred
blade as well, Saya...

293
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:20,583
She fell to them.

294
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:25,708
I won't fail... I promise.

295
00:18:27,583 --> 00:18:30,750
I'll defeat them.
I swear Father...

296
00:18:30,833 --> 00:18:32,458
I'll protect everyone.

297
00:22:16,166 --> 00:22:18,041
I will protect them.

298
00:23:51,041 --> 00:23:53,958
