up late watching TV?

300
00:23:56,458 --> 00:23:58,333
The news or a comedy
show or something?

301
00:23:58,416 --> 00:24:00,250
The shopping channel
or a documentary?

302
00:24:00,333 --> 00:24:02,208
A variety show or
a singing show?

303
00:24:02,291 --> 00:24:04,666
A travel show or a cooking show?

304
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:08,666
Um, I'm not entirely
sure what those things are.

305
00:24:09,375 --> 00:24:12,250
The Kisaragi family
secret is finally revealed...

306
00:24:12,333 --> 00:24:14,166
What could the
shocking truth be?!

